"S\nStephenson Signs\nServices\nOur Work\nReviews\nAbout\nContact\n(423) 746-1804\nFree Quote\nATHENS, TN · SERVING EAST TENNESSEE SINCE 2017\nSigns that get your business noticed.\n\nCustom storefront signs, vehicle wraps, monument signs and banners — designed, built and installed right here in Athens by Kevin, Penny & the team.\n\nGET A FREE QUOTE\n(423) 746-1804\n4.8 / 5\n· 25 Google reviews\n9+ years serving Athens\nLocally owned & operated\n4.8★ Rated\n25+ Google reviews\nFast Turnaround\nQuick, reliable delivery\n9+ Years Local\nTrusted in Athens since 2017\nFree On-Site Quotes\nWe come measure for you\n\nWHAT WE DO\n\nSignage built to bring you business\n\nFrom the first sketch to final installation, we handle every step in-house so your sign looks exactly the way you imagined — and lasts for years.\n\nStorefront Signs\n\nChannel letters, lightboxes and dimensional signage that pulls customers in from the street.\n\nVehicle Graphics & Wraps\n\nTurn every truck, van or trailer into a moving billboard that works around the clock.\n\nMonument Signs\n\nStone-base, illuminated entry signs that give your property a permanent first impression.\n\nBanners & Event Signs\n\nHeavy-duty banners, yard signs and trade-show graphics — printed fast and built to last.\n\nLED & Lighted Signs\n\nEnergy-efficient illuminated signage and retrofits that stay visible day and night.\n\nCustom Design Work\n\nIn-house design from Kevin and the team — your logo, your colors, perfectly executed.\n\nRECENT WORK\n\nA few signs we're proud of\n\nChurches, contractors, restaurants, retail — we've built signage for nearly every kind of business across East Tennessee.\n\nCHANNEL LETTERS\nStorefront Signage\nFULL WRAP\nVehicle Wraps\nILLUMINATED\nMonument Signs\n4.8 on Google\nAthens trusts Stephenson Signs\n\nReal reviews from real customers across East Tennessee.\n\n\"I can't recommend Kevin and Penny enough! They've been serving Athens for 9+ years and really know the sign business inside and out. A fantastic local gem.\"\n\nRavi Kiran Reddy Gudipally\nLocal Guide · 23 reviews\n\n\"Kevin did a great job for the Grace & Mercy people mover and was a pleasure to work with. Very conscientious and friendly.\"\n\nJudy Barnett\nGoogle Review\n\n\"Kevin did great work on the design, and he got my signs quickly! High quality work and fast service with reasonable prices.\"\n\nVerified Customer\nGoogle Review\n\n\"They did a great job for our Church.\"\n\nPaula Barham\nGoogle Review\n\nABOUT THE SHOP\n\nA local shop with 9+ years of craftsmanship.\n\nStephenson Signs has been Athens, Tennessee's go-to sign shop for nearly a decade. Kevin handles design and fabrication. Penny keeps the schedule humming. Together they treat every project — from a single yard sign to a full storefront install — like it's going on their own building.\n\nFamily-owned and operated by Kevin & Penny\nServing Athens, TN and surrounding counties since 2017\nEvery sign designed, built and installed in-house\nHonest pricing and straight answers — every time\nSTART YOUR PROJECT\n9+\nYears in Athens\n4.8★\nGoogle rating\n100%\nIn-house production\n500+\nSigns delivered\n\nGET IN TOUCH\n\nRequest your free quote\n\nTell us a little about your project and we'll get back to you within one business day with ideas, timing and pricing — no pressure, no obligation.\n\nCall us\n(423) 746-1804\nVisit the shop\n219 Tellico Ave\nAthens, TN 37303\nHours\nMon – Fri · 8 AM – 5 PM\nName\nPhone\nEmail\nWhat kind of sign do you need?\nTell us about your project\nSend my quote request\n\nWe typically respond within one business day. Prefer to call? (423) 746-1804\n\nS\nStephenson Signs\n\nAthens, Tennessee's family-owned sign shop. Custom signage, vehicle wraps and banners designed and built in-house since 2017.\n\nVISIT\n219 Tellico Ave, Athens, TN 37303\n(423) 746-1804\nMon – Fri · 8 AM – 5 PM\nEXPLORE\nServices\nOur Work\nReviews\nGet a Quote\n© 2026 Stephenson Signs · Proudly serving Athens, TN"
